---
title: BBQ Pulled Pork Sandos with Gouda, Pickles & Slaw
description: All of the flavors of slow-cooked pulled pork in a matter of minutes makes lunch feel like a picnic, even if you’re at your desk. Succulent, smoky-saucy shredded pork is loaded onto toasted potato buns with nutty gouda, tangy, crisp cabbage slaw, and snappy dill pickle slices. No picnic blanket is required, but do have the napkins handy!
